These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, july, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Birthday        | may | march   | june | july    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: edinburgh, new-york, hannover, colone
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | colone    | edinburgh | hannover | new-york    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, lemonade, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage          | almond-milk | lemonade | sprite    | milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, tea, hot-chocolate
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Beverage   | tea       | milk   | cola    | hot-chocolate  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, handball, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Sport   | swimming | volleyball | skateboarding | handball |

