.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, tea, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, japanese, malaysian
1. the italian is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the italian##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
4. the indonesian is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea      | iced-tea | lemonade | juice |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian     | indonesian  | japanese  |

