.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, march, august
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person eating pepper##2
4. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Birthday    | august     | july | december     | march  |

