.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, lily, tulip
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growstulip##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Flower   | lily | amaryllis | tulip        | daffodil    |

