.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, tea, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, pink, white, chestnut
1. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta   | water   | juice      | tea      |
| Color      | pink | white | chestnut | red |

