.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, vegafina, tiparillo, bluemaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
4. the vegafina-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | bolivar | tiparillo | bluemaster  |
| Transport     | boat   | bike  | train  | motorbike |

