.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, lily, zinnia
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goat, snake
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Flower   | lily | zinnia | amaryllis | marigold |
| Pet           | snake     | dog     | goat   | frog         |

