.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, dubstep, metal, r&b
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the fan of reggae and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | chess         | board-games   | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | dubstep | r&b | reggae   |

