.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, indonesian, pakistani
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, chess, billiard
1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Game     | snooker      | chess       | backgammon | billiard     |

