.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, june, may
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the entrepreneur and the person who's birthday is in april##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| Birthday   | may          | july | april         | june  |

 